quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  65,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  65,1,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jab tum log aurton ko Talaq do to unhen unn ki iddat ke liye Talaq diya karo aur iddat ke zamane ka theek theek shumaar karo, aur Allah se daro jo tumhara rab hai ( zamana iddat mein ) nah tum unhen unn ke gharon se nikalu aur nah woh khud nikleen, ila yeh ke woh kisi Sarih buraiee ki murtakib hon yeh Allah ki muqarrar kardah hade hain, aur jo koi Allah ki hado se tajawaz kere ga woh apne oopar khud zulm kere ga tum nahi jantay, shayad is ke baad Allah ( muwafiqat ki ) koi soorat peda kar day"
  65,2,"phir jab woh apni ( iddat ki ) muddat ke khtama par pohnchain to ya inhen bhallay tareeqay se ( apne nikah mein ) rok ray kho, ya bhallay tareeqay par unn se judda ho jao aur do aisay admion ko gawah bana lau jo tum mein se sahib Adal hon aur ( ae gawah ban'nay walo ) gawahi theek theek Allah ke liye ada karo yeh baatein hain jin ki tum logon ko nasiyaat ki jati hai, har uss shakhs ko jo Allah aur akhirat ke din par imaan rakhta ho jo koi Allah se drtay hue kaam kere ga Allah uss ke liye mushkilaat se niklny ka koi rasta peda kar day ga"
  65,3,aur usay aisay rastay se rizaq day ga jidhar uss ka gumaan bhi nah jata ho jo Allah par bhrosa kere is ke liye woh kaafi hai Allah apna kaam poora kar ke rehta hai Allah ne har cheez ke liye aik taqdeer muqarrar kar rakhi hai
  65,4,aur tumhari aurton mein se jo haiz se mayoos ho chuki hon un ke maamla mein agar tum logon ko koi shak la-haq hai to ( tumhe maloom ho ke ) un ki iddat teen mahinay hai aur yahi hukum unn ka hai jinhein abhi haiz nah aaya ho aur haamla aurton ki iddat ki hadd yeh hai ke unn ka waza hamal ho jaye jo shakhs Allah se daray uss ke maamla mein woh sahoolat peda kar deta hai
  65,5,yeh Allah ka hukum hai jo uss ne tumhari taraf nazil kya hai jo Allah se daray ga Allah is ki buraiyon ko is se daur kar day ga aur is ko bara ajar day ga
  65,6,"unn ko ( zamana iddat mein ) usi jagah rakho jahan tum rehtay ho, jaisi kuch bhi jagah tumhe muyassar ho aur inhen tang karne ke liye un ko nah satao aur agar woh haamla hon to un par uss waqt taq kharch karte raho jab taq un ka waza hamal nah ho jaye phir agar woh tumahray liye ( bachay ko ) doodh pilain to un ki ujrat inhen do, aur bhallay tareeqay se ( ujrat ka maamla ) bahami guft o shaneed se tey kar lau lekin agar tum ne ( ujrat tey karne mein ) aik dosray ko tang kya to bachay ko koi aur aurat doodh pila le gi"
  65,7,"khushaal aadmi apni khushhali ke mutabiq nafqa day, aur jis ko rizaq kam diya gaya ho woh usi maal mein se kharch kere jo Allah ne usay diya hai Allah ne jis ko jitna kuch diya hai is se ziyada ka woh ussay mklf nahi karta baeed nahi ke Allah tang dasti ke baad farakh dasti bhi ataa farma day"
  65,8,kitni hi bastiyan hain jinhon ne apne rab aur is ke Rasolo-n ke hukum se sartabi ki to hum ne un se sakht muhasba kya aur un ko buri terhan saza di
  65,9,unhon ne apne kiye ka maza chakh liya aur unn ka injaam car ghata hi ghata hai
  65,10,Allah ne ( akhirat mein ) un ke liye sakht azaab muhayya kar rakha hai pas Allah se daro ae sahib aqal logo jo imaan laaye ho Allah ne tumhari taraf aik nasiyaat nazil kar di hai
  65,11,"aik aisarasool - jo tum ko Allah ki saaf saaf hadaayat dainay wali ayaat sunataa hai taakay imaan laane walon aur naik amal karne walon ko tarikeon se nikaal kar roshni mein le aeye jo koi Allah par imaan laaye aur naik amal kere, Allah ussay aisijannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi yeh log un mein hamesha hamesha rahen ge Allah ne aisay shakhs ke liye behtareen rizaq rakha hai"
  65,12,"Allah woh hai jis ne saat aasman banaye aur zameen ki qisam se bhi unhi ke manind un ke darmain hukum nazil hota rehta hai ( yeh baat tumhe is liye batayi ja rahi hai ) taakay tum jaan lau ke Allah har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai, aur yeh ke Allah ka ilm har cheez par muheet hai"
